{
  "stem": "13693.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And a few days before, they killed five of our-- of our-- of our boys.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They especially brought the German to put a-- to find out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see, we had intelligence.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we found out what-- what is-- what's going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So first of all, we-- first of all made safe for the Jews what are running away from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because if somebody will expose them to German used to come in, or to burn his house, or even to kill him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So before you notice now the Jews could almost have a freedom over there to move.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The second thing is in here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But now-- but now we have our-- we have already causalities.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We decided already to-- to even up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And every single time we were going over there, they were shooting on us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Who was it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was army [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, in between the Polacks, they had two.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Armia [NON-ENGLISH] and Armia Krajowa;.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Armia [NON-ENGLISH] is-- is the-- is the folks army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Polish-- the Home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Polish Home Army.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The home [? party. ?] This one was with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This one wasn't shooting with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were working with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Armia Krajowa; is-- was under the direction of land army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was under the influence of London.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were rabid anti-Semite.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, first of all, they didn't want-- want us to burn their-- [NON-ENGLISH] from the Polish the nobility, their houses, because the German were over there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we had to burn, it because--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Second thing, their-- their final-- final-- [INAUDIBLE] final goal was to have a free Poland without the Russian.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the thing is-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Niewieniance.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We come into the village.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We surround the village.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had all our [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
